label: DRAW
description: A drawing, a map, a painting, a schematic, or a graphic with labels on a document page.

label: DRAW_L
description: A drawing, a map, a painting, a schematic, or a graphic with an accompanying table or tabular legend on a document page.

label: LINE_HW
description: A table or a filled form containing handwritten text lines on a document page.

label: LINE_P
description: A table or a filled form containing printed text lines on a document page.

label: LINE_T
description: A table or a filled form containing typed text lines on a document page.

label: PHOTO
description: A photo or a photo cutout attached to a document page.

label: PHOTO_L
description: A photo or a photo cutout with an accompanying table or tabular legend on a document page.

label: TEXT
description: A document page with mixed printed and handwritten text styles, such as a newspaper or book cutout with handwritten comments.

label: TEXT_HW
description: A handwritten plain text, handwritten text paragraphs, or handwritten list items on a document page.

label: TEXT_P
description: A printed plain text, printed text paragraphs, or printed list items on a document page.

label: TEXT_T
description: A typed plain text, typed text paragraphs, or typed list items on a document page.
